{"tid":601394,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"每個公司都總有一個老屎忽","createTime":"2018-03-22T07:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T08:56:27.000Z","uid":110275,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5e6827a8277ce5f7770559d47c1178c42fc47f06","tid":601394,"uid":110275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T07:45:16.000Z","msg":"每個公司都總有一個老屎忽<br />\n<br />\n玩排斥、講是非通常都係佢地帶起<br />\n唔鐘意你嘅，喺你背後講你壞話<br />\n同其他同事細聲講、大聲笑，係唔預你<br />\n而你自己諗極都諗唔明 又邊個位唔小心踩親佢條尾<br />\n<br />\n有時候，見到佢地做錯嘢，好心提下<br />\n點知唔該都無聲都算，西面返轉頭，好似我指正返佢錯處，搞到佢不滿咁<br />\n <br />\n俾老細話緊，係都要加鹽加醋，踩多你兩腳<br />\n有問題唔識，請教佢地，答埋啲虛無飄渺嘅答案<br />\n你一做錯？「點解你唔問清楚啊？」<br />\n<br />\n我地呢啲小薯，做到隻狗咁，有時候要ot先搞得掂<br />\n佢？老細一唔喺度，每日lunch食成一個幾鐘後先返黎，之後上下Facebook、玩下網購咁，理得你班小薯含賓州<br />\n但又唔知點解老細一喺度，就好忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有共鳴嘅你一齊9up下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c30fa54bd40d9ca469d327d463cd57298ec586c","tid":601394,"uid":159539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T07:49:20.000Z","msg":"理撚得佢，入世未深先會俾所謂既老屎忽撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff39c3a67d73bb645175d8eb3352c3964db54bc","tid":601394,"uid":110275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9c30fa54bd40d9ca469d327d463cd57298ec586c","tid":601394,"uid":159539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T07:49:20.000Z","msg":"理撚得佢，入世未深先會俾所謂既老屎忽撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T08:02:29.000Z","msg":"Fg表示仲學習緊調整自己心態<br />\nChing有無秘訣"},{"pid":"903a4f7b8c311270b06d4afa217999718b2c2915","tid":601394,"uid":110275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T09:27:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f1b52abeeb9db5d1084e37812d9ab9aa9cd7994","tid":601394,"uid":159539,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cff39c3a67d73bb645175d8eb3352c3964db54bc","tid":601394,"uid":110275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9c30fa54bd40d9ca469d327d463cd57298ec586c","tid":601394,"uid":159539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T07:49:20.000Z","msg":"理撚得佢，入世未深先會俾所謂既老屎忽撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T08:02:29.000Z","msg":"Fg表示仲學習緊調整自己心態<br />\nChing有無秘訣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T09:38:16.000Z","msg":"例如佢串鳩你，你就笑住咁串鳩返佢，唔好剩係傻笑，下下俾佢食撚住佢就當你狗咁撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又例如遇到啲野唔識做，自已睇清楚晒啲野，真係諗過都係唔撚識先問，唔好乜鳩都問一餐，少啲位俾啲屎忽鬼入你波#fs"},{"pid":"f8b805beff4afb8acf78dfe481f990bf26f953e8","tid":601394,"uid":24227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T13:55:08.000Z","msg":"有咩慘得過公司好多老屎忽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又要你奉承佢<br />\n又奉旨hea<br />\n仲要俾佢地點來點去做埋佢個份"},{"pid":"62c553c3ee159389fcb87a1adae5f91270c984d9","tid":601394,"uid":76632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:56:27.000Z","msg":"職場老屎忽=人渣"}]}